The patch files in this directory are designed to be applied on top of CoMD v1.1.

Source code:
    https://github.com/exmatex/CoMD

Installation:

1. Acquire the source:
    wget https://github.com/exmatex/CoMD/archive/master.zip

2. Unpack the source:
    unzip master.zip

3. Change directories to the unpacked files.
    cd CoMD-master

4. Patch nekbone with the patch utility:
    patch -p1 < ../0001-Marked-up-CoMD-code-for-use-with-GEOPM.patch

5. Profit.
